query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_properties,
  COUNT(DISTINCT county) as unique_counties,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN status = 'scheduled' THEN 1 END) as scheduled,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN status = 'in_upset_period' THEN 1 END) as in_upset,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN createdAt >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY) THEN 1 END) as new_last_7_days
FROM properties;
